  => "Top 5 priorities: (1) Unikernel+Virtio+Firecracker 3-6mo, (2) AI primitive + law kernel 6-12mo, (3) Single addr space + zero-copy 3-6mo, (4) Hetzner OEM appliance 12-18mo, (5) Versioned FS + law live-update 6-9mo."
  => "Categories A-P: kernel arch / memory / scheduler / FS / network / drivers / boot / security / AI abstractions / HW targets / tooling / deployment / interop / governance / business / experiments."
  => "n=6 anchor: NOT explicit. 124 items cleanly fit 16 categories — no perfect-number lattice claimed."
